com.ibm.ecm.api.coresdk.collection

Interface IBMECMResultSet<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of items to store in this result set
    All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IBMECMSearchResultSet<T>

    public interface IBMECMResultSet<T>
extends Serializable
    Represents a pageable collection of items.
